00:19.847 --> 00:21.173
I'm with you.

00:22.855 --> 00:24.201
I feel the same.

00:25.935 --> 00:27.576
No doubt about it.

00:29.351 --> 00:30.953
I totally agree.

00:32.845 --> 00:34.205
That's for sure.

